Dialogs.Dialog: Since we're here, why don't we take a picture here？
Rinko
Here？ Great, let's take a picture.
▲小早川＊▲. Do you want to take a picture here？
Rinko
Okay. Let's see what kind of pose you want this time.
▲小早川＊▲. Do you want to take a picture here？
Rinko
.... here？ Yeah, sure.
Rinko
Is there a festival-like pose？ Is it normal？
Rinko
Hmm, so this is what you call a rare shot？
Rinko
"If you don't give me candy, I'll play a trick on you." How about something like this？
Rinko
Since we're here, why don't you take some cultural pictures？
Rinko
Let's take lots of pictures to remember our trip.
Rinko
Hehe. Christmas is a special day, after all. Take some cute pictures.
Rinko
The first photo of the year is Rinko▼
Rinko
It would be a nice memory if we could have our picture taken like this every year.
Rinko
Is this supposed to be a commemorative photo, too？ Don't screw it up, okay？
Rinko
Does it include the surrounding scenery？
Rinko
There are a lot of stalls out there.
Anywhere you want to stop？
Yeah, that one！
Hey, that looks good. ▲メニュー▲.
Yes, it's delicious, want some？
Then...
How do you like it？
Yes, it's good！ Thanks for the food.
Rinko
There are a lot of stalls out there.
Yeah.
Well, since we're here, do you have anything you want to eat？
▲メニュー１▲
▲メニュー２▲
▲メニュー3▲
▲メニュー4▲
▲メニュー5▲
If you're at a food stall, you have to eat this.
Yea, that's good.
Do you want some too, ▲小早川＊▲？
It's delicious, even more so when my boyfriend feeds it to me. Hehe.
Rinko
I've made you a bento, would you like some ....？
Really！ I'll eat it！ I'll eat it！
You're getting way too excited. You're my girlfriend, you should at least eat lunch.
Rinko
Aren't you hungry？ I made you a bento.
▲小早川＊▲ made this？ Of course I'll eat it！
Don't panic so much, your lunch won't escape.
Rinko
I've worked hard to make a bento. You'll eat it, right？
Of course！ I can't wait to see if it's homemade by ▲小早川＊▲.
I'm so glad you're so happy, .... hehe. Now, eat up.
Rinko
Oh, what？
Rinko
It was your birthday. I really wanted to give it to you on that day.
Rinko
Look, it was our anniversary. So that's the present.
Rinko
Christmas present. Because I couldn't give it to you on the day.
Rinko
It's a little late, but here's a Valentine's Day present.
Thanks. Then, from now on too...
Rinko
I see. Hehe, thanks.
Thanks. I'm glad to hear it.
Rinko
I'm glad you're happy with it. Please take good care of it.
Rinko
That's it then. Let's try to meet on the day next year.
Yeah, sorry about that. Thanks for the present.
It's past White Day, but I got you this in return.
Rinko
What, really？
I'm sorry it took so long.
No, I don't mind. You prepared it well, thanks.
(I know it's past White Day, but can we do something now？ ....)
This is a late birthday present ....
Rinko
It's long overdue, though, isn't it？
Sorry！ It's not that I forgot.
I'm not mad at you. But we have to spend next year together. That's a promise.
(By the way, ▲小早川＊▲'s birthday has already passed, can we do something now？ ....)
Rinko
It was before we started dating, and I didn't think I needed to give it to you. .... Well, just in case.
You don't have to worry about it so much, but I'm really happy...
Yeah, I see. Hehe. See you later.
(Even though it was before we started going out, he gave me a decent amount of chocolate: I'll have to think about how to repay you on White Day)
Rinko
Oh, by the way, it's next week. Did you notice？
Let's see....
The anniversary of when we started dating. You haven't forgotten, have you？
That's right！
But since we're going out of our way, let's do something memorable.
Something memorable, huh？
Because if we just go on a normal date, it won't be any different from usual.
Let's buy something matching to commemorate the date！
What？ That's so embarrassing. Rejected.
I see, ....
Let's think about it some more, it's fun to discuss things like this.
Yeah.
Rinko
For our anniversary, it's still nice. Matching goods.
Oh, I see. What should we get then, ....？
Well, I'd like to go to the mall with you tomorrow and we can decide together. How about ....？
Choose a gift while discussing it, huh？ ....Yeah, I like that.
Right？ I think it would be fun.
But why did you change your mind？ You rejected it before.
It's just that... I guess... You probably have your own thoughts on the matter. And when the day actually approaches, you feel that way too, don't you？
What do you mean by that？
It's the .... lovey mood.
Rinko
▲主人公＊▲.
▲小早川＊▲. Have you figured out where to start going around？
Not yet. Aren't you getting a little carried away？
You think so？
You don't have to be in such a hurry. You want to take your time when choosing a gift.
.... I guess that's true. Let's take our time.
Rinko
▲主人公＊▲.
Yo, ▲小早川＊▲.
You're late. I was waiting for you...
But I'm not late...？
Even if you're not late, don't make your girlfriend wait for you.
Sorry about that ....
Good. So, let's take a look around, shall we？
▲小早川＊▲.
Rinko
▲主人公＊▲. Hey, have you decided what you're going to do？
Not yet. What about Kobayakawa*▲？
Well.... I don't want to waste my time thinking about this.
Let's just go to some stores and see what we can find.
Yea. Let's go.
What about a key ring .... or something？
Rinko
Carve your initials or something？ It's not a tourist attraction. Rejected.
A plate engraved with two names.
It's not like it's a wedding gift.
I'm kidding. What's your opinion▲小早川＊▲？
I thought I'd check out the boyfriend's taste. Observation.
I told you it's a keepsake for the two of us, so we'll choose it together, right？
I can't help it. So, why don't we go over there and take a look？
Hey, I got a good one.
After all, a girl's opinion is important. I never would have chosen if it was just me.
Rinko spent a lot of time choosing it for you, so you should cherish it. Okay？
If I'm going to buy something, I want it to stay with me.
Rinko
Yeah. But I don't want to buy a set. Rejected.
No？ But It's a classic, right？
I don't like it because it's standard. It's like you're trying to appeal to a couple.
Can't we even buy matching things？
It's acceptable if they are casually matching. It's a matter of taste.
It's difficult to order from ....
It's your boyfriend's role to worry about his girlfriend. Do your best.
Yea, this is good.
It took me a while, but I'm glad I chose a good one. Do you like it too, Kobayakawa？
It's not bad, right？ I have to acknowledge my boyfriends efforts, too.
When it comes to gifts, I guess flowers are the standard.
Rinko
I'd be happy with any present from my boyfriend.
Well, since we're here, let's choose together. Is there anything you want？
No, not really ....
Today, I'll listen to whatever ▲小早川＊▲ wants.
It's not just about things. .... I want to take my time looking around today. .... Let's hold hands.
Look around slowly？
Yes. It's boring if you just pick a present and that's it. Right？
Hehe. It was fun.
▲小早川＊▲, it's hard to decide on a present, isn't it？
That's good, because I was able to buy it. It's called a good result.
(▲小早川＊▲ while choosing. He looked like he was having fun. ....)
I hope we can celebrate our anniversary together like this again next year.
Rinko
Next year too？ .... As long as we don't change our mind.
Rinko's feelings will never change, though.
Hmm？ What did you say？
No, I didn't say anything. You misheard. It was your imagination. .... Oh, I'll just send it here.
You know, thanks .... Today.. was fun.
.... yeah.
Yes, it was.
Goodbye already, huh？
Don't look at me like we're saying goodbye for life. You can meet me anytime. We'll see each other tomorrow, ...., and forever after that.
▲小早川＊▲. Maybe you don't like the present？
Rinko
That's not what I meant. After all, you want me to say it in words, don't you？
You don't think it's enough just to give a present, do you？
That's not true.
Well, then, don't you have something to say on special occasions？
Oh, I see. ...●You know, I'm really glad that▲小早川＊▲ is my girlfriend.
Rinko is too. So, why don't you just....？ Before someone else comes along.
What？ ... Ok.
Thanks for today. It was a day to remember.
Thanks too. I hope we can celebrate like this again next year.
Yea. See you ...
Rinko
The shopkeeper asked about us. He said, "Are you a couple？"
That was a bit embarrassing.
There's nothing to be embarrassed about. It's not wrong.
Huh？ I thought▲小早川＊▲ would be more embarrassed.
Not at all. ....... You're already here.
You know, Rinko and I are lovers, aren't we？ Then .... kiss me goodbye.
What？ ....Ok....
If you don't hurry, someone will come.
Are you... finished？
About today. You can do it anytime you want, because I'll always love you, ▲小早川＊▲.
Ah, you're such an idiot. Don't say that. ....
Hahaha. See you later.
Rinko
Your birthday is coming up soon, right？
That's what I thought.
.... maybe you don't even remember your own birthday？
I do, but I'm not really conscious of it.
Birthdays are special days, but if you keep acting like that, they'll just pass by like any other day.
How can I say this？ Aren't you going to celebrate with me？
Do you want me to celebrate？
Well, I guess I'd be happy if my .... girlfriend celebrates with me.
I don't know. I'll think of something.
Wow. I've already had "boyfriend's birthday" marked in my schedule book for a long time.
Rinko
Please keep your schedule open tomorrow night.
Tomorrow night ....？
It's your birthday, right？ Have you made any plans by any chance？
Not yet. Is ▲小早川＊▲ going to celebrate with us？
I told you I'd think about it. So, please wait for me at your place.
Your place？ I thought you were going to ask me to go somewhere.
You can do that anytime you want. There's only one birthday a year, you know.
That's true, but .... what are you going to do？
That's for you to find out that day. I'll make it a birthday you'll never forget.
(An unforgettable birthday. I'm looking forward to it)
▲小早川＊▲.... What's in that shopping bag？
Rinko
It's your birthday, right？
Could it be ....▲小早川＊▲ is cooking for us？
What's with the surprise？ I see. You don't want to eat it. Then I'll stop making it.
I was just surprised because it was sudden. Of course I want to eat it！
I'll borrow your kitchen then.
(I wonder what kind of food she'll cook for me)
Yes, Rinko's homemade food.... Ah, don't rush
Because ▲小早川＊▲made it, I wanted to eat it right away.
You don't need to panic, it won't run away, just taste it and eat it.
▲小早川＊▲. I've been waiting for you. .... Huh？ A shopping bag？
Rinko
A ready-made meal on your birthday would be sad, wouldn't it？
This means....▲小早川＊▲ is going to cook for me？
That's what I mean. Can I borrow your kitchen, ....？
Yes. You can use it any way you like.
.... what？ I don't like it when people stare at me like that.
Well, yeah！ I'll look forward to seeing the finished product.
Yes. A home-made dish specially prepared by Rinko.
Wow, isn't there something elaborate today？
It's .... well, it's your birthday. I can't guarantee the taste, but .... what do you think？
▲小早川＊▲？ Welcome.
Rinko
Heh. Thanks for waiting. I've been shopping and I'm late.
Shopping is ....
I told you that I would make your birthday unforgettable. So tonight, Rinko will cook for you ▼
Really？ That would be great.
I'll put a lot of effort into making it. Look forward to it.
(I'm looking forward to today's ▲小早川＊▲ because they seem really into it)
Bam！
Wow, this is amazing. Did ▲小早川＊▲ make all these？
Yes. I followed the recipe exactly, but I hope it suits your .... palate. Do you want to try it？
It was really delicious.▲小早川＊▲, your cooking skills have improved, haven't they？
Rinko
I see. I'm glad it suited your taste.
And that thing behind you, could it be a present？
Yes, but... Why did you have to find it before I gave it to you？ ....Ok, here.
Because I don't receive them very often.
Even Rinko was thinking about the timing. But you gave it anyway.
I'm so lucky to have my girlfriend's homemade food and gifts on my birthday.
You're exaggerating. If you're that happy, you're lying.
It's not a lie, I'm really happy. Thank you, ▲小早川＊▲.
You said you couldn't guarantee the taste, but it was delicious.
Rinko
Yes. It was good. .... And then there's this.
A present？ Are you sure？
It's your birthday, so of course it's ok.
You made me a home-cooked meal, and now you're giving me a present. I'm very happy.
Are you really that happy？
Of course, anyone would be happy if their girlfriend did this much for them.
I see. If that's so, then maybe it was worth the effort.
Yeah, it was a great birthday. Thanks for that.
That's because you're my girlfriend, so you deserve it.
The food was delicious, whether it suited my palate or not.
Rinko
It was good. .... Actually, I was worried about what would happen if it didn't turn out well.
And hey, ....
Yes, here. A birthday present.
You made me a home-cooked meal, and now you're giving me a present？
Because it's your birthday, isn't it strange if you don't get a present？
I was really happy with just the home-cooked meal.
I hope you like it...
▲小早川＊▲ picked it for me, didn't she？ Then how could I not like it？
Really？ Well then, take good care of it forever, okay？
Rinko
Well, I guess it's time to go home.
I'm sorry to keep you up at this hour. I'll walk you home.
Yeah, but it's ok. I can go home alone.
.... have a safe trip home.
Yeah.... is that it？
That's all ....
You won't go？ Even though your girlfriend's leaving？
Ok, I'm leaving.
Thanks for today. It was a good birthday for me.
.... I'm glad you're happy. Bye.
Rinko
Ah .... I have to go home soon.
Is it that time already？
I know you don't want to leave, but you can't just not go home, right？
That's true, but ....
Having a lonely boyfriend can be difficult, really.
I'm lonely and .... well, I'm lonely.
Why don't you do what you always do when you're lonely？ Come on... give me a hug....
What do you think？ Now you won't be lonely, will you？
Yeah. This might be the best birthday present I've ever had.
Why do you say that .... Well, I hope you're happy. Bye.
Rinko
Is it that time already？
Hey, you'd better go home soon, your parents will be worried.
Don't act old.
You know, before I leave, I have a question: .... How was your birthday？
I was happy to celebrate with ▲小早川＊▲.
I'm glad you were happy. So, ...., can I ask for a favor from Rinko this time？
A favor？ What is it？
A reward. .... Do you... want to kiss？
Heh. Thanks.
....have a safe trip home.
Yes. See you later.
Rinko
You know, you didn't forget... did you？ It's about time.
What is it？
....You really don't remember？ I can't believe you forgot your girlfriend's birthday.
I'm just kidding. How could I forget▲小早川＊▲'s birthday？
.... Sorry, I guess I prompted you. But you don't have to do anything special.
What about a party or something？
When I was little, they used to throw me a party every year. ....
Let's do it then.
I don't want to make a big deal out of it. I'm fine with spending time with you rather than doing anything special.
(Are you sure you want to do that ....？)
▲小早川＊▲. For example, is there any place you'd like to visit on your birthday？
Rinko
It's so sudden, I don't have anything in particular.
Even though it's your birthday？
Well then, why don't we go to karaoke？
That's the same as always.
Isn't that good？ Ok, How about we go to the arcade and play some games？ And finish it off with a live performance.
How about a full course of Rinko's favorite foods？ We don't usually get to go to all of them.
Is that what you want？
That's enough. It's not often that you get to experience a day full of your favorite things.
(If▲小早川＊▲ wants to go, then I guess that's fine)
Rinko
▲主人公＊▲. Sorry to keep you waiting.
▲小早川＊▲, happy birthday.
Hey, thanks. Let's start with karaoke, shall we？
That's the thing. Are you sure you want to go on the same date as usual today？
I said it's fine. And it's not the same.
It's more like an endurance race, starting with karaoke and ending with live music.
That's what I mean. We're wasting time.
You could have told us more about places you can't usually go.
It's okay. I just joined a new game, and I wanted to be the first to try it out.
It doesn't have to be on your birthday, does it？
Are you unhappy？
Well, if it makes ▲小早川＊▲ happy, then it's fine.
That's what I mean. I'm going to give you a good beating today.
Just because it's my birthday, I'd like you to be gentle with me.
Hehe. What should I do？
Rinko
Hmmm, you sang！
Don't skip .... Are you okay after this？
I'm fine. Let's go to the game center then！
Hey, hey, hey！
All right, all right.
If you don't hurry up, the live performance will start.
Yo, okay, ....
Oh, that was good. That's the best performance I've ever seen.
That was good ....
Hmm, what's up？
After singing so much at karaoke, you shouted at a live performance. Your voice is already rattled.
You're so sloppy！
▲小早川＊▲ doesn't look tired at all. He's been jumping around the whole show, right？
It's a comfortable tiredness. I'm sure Rinko could handle another karaoke session after this.
(Don't get me started on that. .... It's been a slammed day.)
Rinko
....It's kind of nice to be celebrated on my birthday.
But can't they celebrate it at▲小早川＊▲'s house too？
That's it. But spending your birthday with your boyfriend is special, isn't it？
Is that what it is？
That's the way it is. So, thanks... I had a great time today.
.... haha.
Rinko, did I say something funny？
Saying something like that with a frown on your face, ▲小早川＊▲ .... haha.
Oh, you laughed again！ I'm going to get angry now, okay？
I'm sorry, I won't laugh again！
Rinko
Hey. How was your date today？
....Yeah, it was fun.
You aren't pushing yourself, are you？
I'm not pushing it, but I'm also .... tired.
But you had fun, right？
Yes, that's for sure！
Then that's okay. If that's the case, that's fine, because I was wondering if only Rinko was having fun.
It was fun to see ▲小早川＊▲enjoying himself. Even now.
I would be embarrassed if he stared at me that much.
Haha. You don't have to be so shy.
Rinko
Sorry about today.
What？ Why？
I just thought I might have dragged you around a bit.
That's not true. It's my birthday, so as long as ▲小早川＊▲ is happy, that's all that matters.
But you must be really tired, huh？
Well, .... a little. But it was more fun than that, really.
That's fine, then....
Hmm？
Should we go to karaoke again？
Rejected！
Dang it！
That's right, I have to give you your birthday present.
Rinko
.... for Rinko？
Who else？
.... yeah, thanks.
That's right, I have to give you your birthday present.
Rinko
You don't have to worry about it. I was just happy that you went out with me today.
It's fine, just tell me how you feel.
....Ok. Thanks.
Yes, I have to give you your birthday present.
Rinko
For Rinko？ What is it？
I hope you like it.
Hehe. Thanks. You don't mind if I take a look inside, do you？
Rinko
That's nice！ You have good sense. I like it.
Rinko
You know exactly what Rinko likes, heh！ Thanks.
Rinko
Rinko, this is what I wanted. You got it. Thanks.
Rinko
Isn't this kind of a good idea？ Thanks.
Rinko
Is this what you think of Rinko？ Heh, maybe it's a new discovery.
Rinko
You've thought hard about this. Thanks.
Rinko
What？ ....You know, this .... can't be helped.
Rinko
I thought you'd be a little more understanding of what I like ....
Rinko
I know you tried hard to choose the best one for me. .... Yeah, It's the thought that counts.
Rinko
Yeah. Are you going to follow me into the house？ Here's fine.
I see. I'll see you later.
Yes, see you.
▲主人公＊▲.
▲小早川＊▲？
You know, if it's just for a little while longer, I have time. And, you know, ....
Let's finish for today. Hey, can we celebrate .... Rinko's birthday again next year？
You don't have to ask that, do you？
I see. I'll see you next time ....
Rinko
Here is fine.
I see. .... Hmm, what？
You know, .... aren't you supposed to do that when you say goodbye？
What？
You could have led with more.
.... yeah. Good night.
Good night. Also, it was a lot of fun today. Thanks.
Today's ▲小早川＊▲ is being awfully honest.
Yeah....？ I hope next year's birthday is as fun as this one.
I'll start thinking about it now. So long, good night.
Rinko
So, here we are. Goodbye, I guess. ....
You don't have to say it like it's a lifelong goodbye.
Because this day has been so much fun, I'm going to miss you when we say goodbye.
I hope next year, and the birthdays after that, will always be fun days like this....
I'm sure it will be.
Yeah, I guess so. Hey, .... can I .... for a minute？
Heh. I'm relieved. Maybe I'll have a good dream today now.
See you later.
Yes, good night.
Rinko
The bamboo branches were displayed in the town. Tanabata？
Well, it's already next week.
Hey. What are you going to ask for？
What about .... you ▲小早川＊▲？
Rinko's is a secret.
Then mine is also a secret.
Oh, that's not fair. .... Ah, That's right. Let's bring the strips of paper which we wrote our wishes on. That's good, right？
Then .... though it's a bit embarrassing.
No. We have to show each other. Okay？ Absolutely.
Oh, okay.
Did you bring the strips of paper with you？
Rinko
Just in case.
Which one is ▲小早川＊▲'s wish....
Oh no, don't look at it. Here, where's your strip of paper？
You see, here it is.
Rinko
▲小早川＊▲？
Well, this is .... What if other people see it？
They can't see it, so what does it matter？
Stupid ....... hehe.
Hey... here.
Rinko
....Is this what you wish ....？
Yes. Did I do something wrong？
It's Tanabata. It's Orihime and Hikoboshi. Think about the situation a little more.
(Did I make you feel bad ....？)
Actually, I forgot to prepare the .... strips, didn't I？
Rinko
What？ Really？ .... I can't believe it. You promised.
I'm sorry！
Sorry is not good enough. Write it here right now.
Rinko
Look, look. That area is the Milky Way, isn't it？
So, that's Hikoboshi and .... that is Orihime, right？
I'm glad it was sunny. It's good that two people who love each other can see each other properly.
They're so lucky to be able to meet whenever they want.
Can I come closer？
....Yes. What's up？
I just want to be closer to the people I love. I don't want to be separated from them.
And one more favor, okay？
It's Tanabata, so yes. What kind of request？
You know, let's .... kiss ....？
Hehe. Did Hikoboshi and Orihime see us？
They're already preparing for the festival at the Juhano Shrine, but I guess it's that time of year already.
Rinko
It's already next month.
Should we go together？
Umm, Rinko will go with friends.
Why？ Why don't you go with me？
Because there is a legend about the Juhano Festival.
Legend？ I think it's something about the god of love at the shrine.
Yes. But if two couples visit the shrine during the festival, the gods will get jealous and break them up.
It could just be a legend, but you never know.
(I think you're overthinking this ....)
Rinko
It's the Juhano Festival today. I heard it's already been crowded since this morning.
Well, ▲小早川＊▲, are you going with your friends？
I don't know, we're all a bit confused. ....
I knew it. Let's go together after all.
.... so what if the legend is true？
Do you know the couple who broke up like the legend says ▲小早川＊▲ ？
Hmmm, I don't know ....
Right？ Do you think our love can be defeated by such legend？
Don't you feel embarrassed when you say .... love？ Oh well, It can't be helped. If you want to go that far, I'll go with you.
Then, it's settled. See？
Rinko
Here you go.
What？ Why are you so jittery and .... weird？
No. You look really good in your yukata, Kobayakawa.
Heh. Thanks.
Hey. Let's go over there next time. They're having goldfish scooping.
Oh, come on. Don't run too fast.
Hey, hey. Are you good at scooping goldfish？
Well, I don't know. I think I'm better at it than▲小早川＊▲.
You know what they say. I'm not going to go easy on you.
Rinko
It's almost the end of the Juhano Festival.
That went by so fast.
It says there will be fireworks on the last day.
Well, that's nice. Let's go then.
Yes, I want to see them with you.
But can you not let go of Rinko's hand for the whole festival？
Of course. I don't want her to get lost or anything.
That's not what I meant. ....Well, if you're not going to let go, that's fine.
(Maybe it's ▲小早川＊▲. Are you still worried about the legend of the Juhano Shrine: ....？)
Rinko
Hey, there you are. ....What？
I thought today's yukata was really cute.
You don't get anything even if you flatter me.
